room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by The Escape Room Woodbridge in New Brunswick
review: Thank you sooo much Barry and Eric for helping to make my birthday celebration a success! My friends and I had an amazing time. You were so friendly, welcoming and accommodating. The Museum Heist was challenging yet tons of fun! I'll definitely be back!
